  <p>Mendoza sets itself apart from other wine regions with its proximity to the Andes providing purity of environment, intense UV light and a harsher climate through which the grapes are forced to struggle, creating albeit a far more interesting and natural fruit driven palate.</p>
  <p>From Salta and Cafayate in the North, down to Patagonia and the Rio Negro in the south, we have sourced our wines to represent all different regions and climates in Argentina.  Many of our wines are also personally sourced and therefore are only available at San Telmo.</p>
